Date: Sun, 24 May 2026 17:37:26 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] shipping: fetch real values from brand_shipping table

Replaces hardcoded freeAt/ship in STORES with a brand-keyed lookup
into the brand_shipping table populated by the new shipping scraper.
PrefsModal now shows real verified shipping policy or "not verified
yet" instead of fabricated thresholds.
